9# 🌌 Vabrint ESP Library

A lightweight and fully customizable ESP library for Roblox.

Created by:

- 🎥 [Mrpopcat14](https://www.youtube.com/@mrpopcat14)
- 🕹️ Discord: `91yd`

---

## 🚀 Loadstring

```lua
loadstring(game:HttpGet("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Rx1m/Vabrint-Library/refs/heads/main/Loader.lua"))()
```

Once loaded, it exposes the global `ESP` table.

---

## ⚙️ Customization Options

Below are all customization options with separate code blocks for easy copy-paste.

---

### 🎨 Box Color

- Default: RGB rainbow
- To use a static color:

```lua
ESP:SetColor(Color3.fromRGB(255, 0, 0)) -- Red
```

---

### 🧊 Box Toggle

```lua
ESP:SetShowBoxes(true) -- enable
ESP:SetShowBoxes(false) -- disable
```

---

### 🏷️ Name Display

```lua
ESP:SetShowNames(true) -- enable name tags
ESP:SetShowNames(false)
```

---

### 🧭 Tracers

```lua
ESP:SetShowTracers(true)
ESP:SetShowTracers(false)
```

---

### ❤️ Health Bar

```lua
ESP:SetShowHealth(true) -- enable
ESP:SetShowHealth(false)
```

---

### 🩸 Health Bar Style

**Match ESP color:**

```lua
ESP:SetHealthColorMode("match")
```

**Custom color (based on percentage):**

```lua
ESP:SetHealthColorMode("custom")
ESP:SetHealthColorFunction(function(healthPercent)
    if healthPercent > 0.7 then
        return Color3.fromRGB(0, 255, 0) -- green
    elseif healthPercent > 0.3 then
        return Color3.fromRGB(255, 165, 0) -- orange
    else
        return Color3.fromRGB(255, 0, 0) -- red
    end
end)
```

---

### ✅ Enable ESP

```lua
ESP:Enable()
```

### ❌ Disable ESP

```lua
ESP:Disable()
```

---

## 📦 File Structure

```
esp.lua           <- Main ESP source code
README.md         <- Documentation (this file)
```

